              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Bismuth of high purity, shown by chemical analysis",
                "to contain < 0.001 % of thorium and < 0.01 % of uranium",
                "was used. The metal plates used in the experiments",
                "measured 10 x 15 x 2 mm and weighed up to 2 g. The",
                "plates were wrapped in aluminum foil 25 microns thick",
                "and were bombarded by a 0.2 to 0.4 mu-ampere proton",
                "current."
